    <h2 class="center"><%= t('meta.open_core') %></h2>
    <hr>
    <p>We believe that the open sharing of knowledge - especially that for growing food and taking care of our environment - can significantly raise our quality of life and reduce our negative impact on the earth. As a project with openness at our core, we’re striving towards organizational and financial transparency; accessibility of our data and source code; and openness to all ideas, people, and perspectives. We invite you to join in our thinking and explore these specific actions we are taking:</p>
