        <li>Anyone can help us develop OpenFarm and we strongly encourage it; here is our <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/13_VQDOm8HpM49Ql3HyNfL9ut5JlqbLEDA9yEk5OqgqU/edit?usp=sharing">development roadmap</a></li>

